  "content_id": "3a5677ee-a31d-4620-b7de-6925bf1b1b27",
  "description": "Small commercial vessels must be registered, surveyed and inspected to meet UK safety laws - registering a boat, surveys and inspections",
  "details": {
    "body": "\n<div class=\"summary\">\n<p>You must have small commercial boats surveyed to make sure that they comply with UK safety laws.</p>\n</div>\n\n<p>Any boat thatâ€™s not a pleasure vessel is considered to be a commercial boat.</p>\n\n<p>Before going to sea, the boat must be tested on its:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>safety</li>\n  <li>construction</li>\n  <li>control systems</li>\n  <li>onboard machinery</li>\n  <li>electrical equipment</li>\n</ul>\n\n<h2 id=\"register-a-small-commercial-vessel\">Register a small commercial vessel</h2>\n\n<p>Contact the UK Ship Register (<abbr title=\"UK Ship Register\">UKSR</abbr>) for more information on registering small commercial vessels under 100 gross tonnes (GT).</p>\n\n<div class=\"contact\">\n<p><strong>UK Ship Register</strong> <br>\nEmail: <a href=\"mailto:comm_registry@mcga.gov.uk\">comm_registry@mcga.gov.uk</a> <br>\nTelephone: 029 2044 8800 <br>\n<a href=\"/call-charges\">Find out about call charges</a></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"address\"><div class=\"adr org fn\"><p>\n\nUK Ship Register\n<br>Anchor Court\n<br>Keen Road\n<br>Cardiff \n<br>CF24 5JW\n<br>\n</p></div></div>\n\n<p>Contact the Maritime and Coastguard Agency (<abbr title=\"Maritime and Coastguard Agency\">MCA</abbr>) if you want to register a <a href=\"/uk-ship-register-for-merchant-ship-and-bareboat-charter-100gt\">commercial vessel over 100 GT.</a></p>\n\n<h2 id=\"small-commercial-vessel-surveys\">Small commercial vessel surveys</h2>\n\n<p>Your boat will be surveyed to one of the following codes of practice:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>the safety of small commercial motor vessels</li>\n  <li>the safety of small commercial sailing vessels</li>\n  <li>the safety of small workboats and pilot boats</li>\n  <li>the safety of small vessels in commercial use for sport or pleasure operating from a nominated departure point</li>\n  <li>small vessels in commercial use for sport or pleasure, workboats and pilot boats - alternative construction standards</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>Read more information on <a href=\"/government/publications/small-craft-codes\">small craft codes</a>.</p>\n\n",
    "external_related_links": [

    ]
  },
